Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是巴迪的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你又把身體借我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想變回巴迪的時候就變回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  這次是我主動要你殺我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服和頭髮顏色記得弄普通一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑的衣服我帶來了  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換衣服去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是阿留多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在到處找流落街頭的阿留多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人網路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來不像是單純的難民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個怪光事件有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是軍隊特務一類的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這地球上進行可疑兵器的實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  你也不過是個棄子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟連神祇廳都行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回聯邦也肯定是蹲監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要留在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,東京暫時是沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！我們還得吃飯啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  東京不行了就去關西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關西  並且是在神戶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開個露天慈善演唱會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼選有田紫苑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟還有恐怖襲擊的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在大牌點的根本不會接演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就選一個小眾的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一有田紫苑火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們公司來說也是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  怎麼又是那個寫真偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我絲毫沒有違抗神祇廳的計劃的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了哦  你得到休假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你消息可真快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咱混那麼久還是有點門路的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始  暫時就作為有田紫苑替我賺錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒的房租你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有零花錢你有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有最喜歡的壽司吃你活得下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球生活是需要錢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你有錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就那點勉強的生活費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}茶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狂…狂戰士殺手巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子是我們公司的藝人  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那個…我是卡貝拉  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這孩子做你的經理人兼跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做這傢伙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你囉  小卡貝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女高中生的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼久沒工作了  不愧是專業的啊  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說下週有慈善演唱會？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自…自行車俱樂部？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個吧  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an3\fad(200,200)}{\fn@方正黑体_GBK}{\frz270}把愛灑滿整個宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會去看的  加油吧  小紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你還沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之是下週的五六七
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地點是神戶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  等…等等～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,集合時間是早上六點半  東京站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近還好嗎  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:07:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡的一週轉眼就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是女高  所以覺得有點不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但習慣了還是個很有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的過得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牧場的生活也總算是習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還穿著這衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今早說好要看牛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不聽你任性的藉口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把衣服換了到牛棚去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京長大的大小姐連看牛都不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點  要不牛都跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我們報道研  絕不能無視這次的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你的而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑我們沒辦法調查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯合國都介入調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今原因仍無法確定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,網上甚至有傳言是使用了化學武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說啦  竟然相信這種謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俗話說無風不起浪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無風起浪就是謠言了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不被這樣的謠言所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向人們傳達正確的情報才是報導的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是早宮  說得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,週末到品川去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不到現場就無法瞭解真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,週末？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行  我有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有小紫苑的演唱會  在神戶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小紫苑好萌  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你也是去小紫苑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會  是親戚邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶！果然是去小紫苑的演唱會吧？千川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神戶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去神戶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學的新住址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過一會去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這可真讓人期待吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,導遊手冊上說有唐人街呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是剛吃完便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想嘗嘗各種地球的食物喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也拿到零花錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是這  這家旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就這家旅館的時代感不太一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大白天居然漆黑一片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個人住這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概三天  足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…有自由活動時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  晚飯前一定要回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沉浸在旅遊觀光中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上還要開會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an3\fs20}禁止給豬餵食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  我說  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為功沒出息我就帶你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想確認中杉小姐平安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香  再不去打掃羊棚  羊就都要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學  說是遠房親戚  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要軟冰淇淋的話請去那邊的小賣店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來你的東西好像很重呢  我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  因為我擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是從東京來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又鬆又軟  就像洋娃娃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐一個人來神戶的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方真美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我最喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你很快就要回東京對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易相見卻又要立刻分別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很失禮吧  說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還能再來找你玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就澡堂很大  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說巴迪  明天真的還去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功你覺得沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓中杉小姐打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？要我怎麼幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,東京的大小姐還真是高高在上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是在牧場看完牛羊後再來這裡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  大小姐做這種活還真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像在勉強自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實很寂寞吧  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是條好狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到你還會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我身邊的人應該都離我而去才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人都離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候父母就因事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候很傷心  很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知什麼時候連那種感覺都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得沒有爸爸媽媽是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前最喜歡的爺爺也去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也肯定會在哪天被忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕那樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我寧可一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想喜歡上任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  也在很久以前失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時很寂寞  很不甘心  無法原諒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那時候  有人陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉小姐身邊一定也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得人與各種人的相遇是最重要  最幸福的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有分別的一天  也一定會在某處…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某處…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴隆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉小姐  別離開我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是勞拉I型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是從聯邦來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住這傢伙就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  我想吃神戶的牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  放開了去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…  可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把那孩子交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不許再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近我就殺了這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  她呼叫宇宙船了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  你想救中杉小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就幫我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣衝向傀儡機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我沒義務向你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  被人救了感謝才合乎常理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有感情  我真感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼中杉小姐會被傀儡機器人給盯上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她曾是硫加的宿主  這理由足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別故弄玄虛  全告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宿主體內有可能殘留著硫加的微小碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也認為這個可能性非常低
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是聯邦裡有人賭上這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後派她來到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,調查下這個傀儡機器人就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船也被逮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覬覦硫加計劃的傢伙已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我當誘餌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝您的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是誘餌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為我對小夜香小姐太苛刻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為醫生說儘量讓她多戶外活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她才剛失去爺爺  應該更溫柔地對她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴隆  怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川…君？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好嗎  不和中杉小姐說話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  千川那傢伙！總是不守時
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.78,0:25:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.22,0:25:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像有困難  你想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.03,0:25:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.84,0:25:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.26,0:25:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.28,0:25:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  奈多流
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.76,0:25:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  第一次買這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.23,0:25:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位姐姐在擔心我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你這麼熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.57,0:25:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡  我沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.78,0:25:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄一很喜歡這個的  一定會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.77,0:26:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.56,0:26:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  千川！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.51,0:26:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  她已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.44,0:26:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好道歉哦  誰讓你睡過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.58,0:26:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你神氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.79,0:26:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  千川  你這人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.37,0:26:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直一直那麼慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.53,0:26:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好遵守約定！
